I found that the problem is that the position of <torch/tensor.h> has been changed , it's in <torch/serialize/tensor.h> now. I changed the code and solved my prolem.
 
 Hello, i meet the same problems, i want to know how to change the code? than you

  said " Please change torch/torch.h to torch/extension.h. " .But it didn't solve my problem. I found that the error was that <torch/tensor.h> couldnot be found, so I changed all the "#include <torch/tensor.h>" in cpp files to "#include <torch/serialize/tensor.h>". Maybe the position of "tensor.h" can be different, you can change the path in your own system. Hope this will help.
